<br>
As will the better gear with focus effects.<br>
<br>
We are used to having spells be hard to obtain.  There is at least one Shaman in my guild that still needs torpor, some wizzies need Sunstrike, etc.  You kill dragons and cross your fingers.<br>
<br>
The poorly thought out aspect of the Luclin implementation is that there is no farmable area where you can get a fair representation of the level 60 spells.  In Kunark you could.  In Veloius...well there really was only one 60 spell for us in Velious...but that dropped in a lot of places including non boss mobs.<br>
<br>
With Luclin, level 60 spells drop only from named mobs in specific zones.  These mobs have timers of 3 to 7ish days, and are usually killed within a half hour or so of spawning.  There is no opportunity here to go farm most of the spells.<br>
<br>
Ok there is the priest ring in akheva for some priest spells.  But as far as I know that is the only spot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showPrevMessage?topicID=710.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showNextMessage?topicID=710.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=710.topic&index=3><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.emailToFriend?topicID=710.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.threadControl?topicID=710.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=710.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=710.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovespells">Spells<option value="thedruidsgrovequests">Quests<option value